Performing Arts Tour | Ch.3: "Cheetah the Aerialist"

Cheetah Platt and Rhiann Woodyard, two truly incredible acrobats were featured in the 3rd production of our Performing Arts Tour. I wanted to emphasize the insane gravity defying poses that Aerialists demonstrate during performances—poses that require both focus and the utmost amount of trust in one another. The strength and stamina is nothing compared to the willpower to hold on. 

Follow our short behind the scenes documentary series, and watch as each production gets better (and crazier!). New uploads every Sunday! 
Next week? A pair of ballerinas, and some unexpected surprises in Albuquerque, New Mexico.

Facebook.com/danieldearcophotography

Special thanks to the videographer Leo Omar Moring
